sec.p:
The micro-averaged Recall, Precision, and F1-Score can be computed using Equations 1, 2, and 3, respectively:
\begin{equation*}
\begin{gathered}
\text { Recall }_{\text {micro }}=\frac{\sum_{k \in L} T P_{k}}{\sum_{k \in L} T P_{k}+F N_{k}} \tag{1}\\
\text { Precision }_{\text {micro }}=\frac{\sum_{k \in L} T P_{k}}{\sum_{k \in L} T P_{k}+F P_{k}} \tag{2}\\
F 1-\text { Score }_{\text {micro }}=\frac{2 \cdot \text { Precision }_{\text {micro }} \cdot \text { Recall }_{\text {micro }}}{\text { Precision }_{\text {micro }}+\text { Recall }_{\text {micro }}}
\end{gathered}
\tag{3}
\end{equation*}
Where:

•
$T P_{k}$ is the number of true positives for class $k$,
•
$F P_{k}$ is the number of false positives for class $k$,
•
$F N_{k}$ is the number of false negatives for class $k$,
•
and $L$ is the set of all labels (i.e., the 10 Cancer Hallmarks).
